        </table></div><div class="header-trail" style="font-size: 12px"><div title="trail"><a href="?keys=FGEA-print&amp;mode=TOC">The Founding Era Collection</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print&amp;mode=TOC">The Adams Papers Digital Edition</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print-06&amp;mode=TOC">Papers of John Adams</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-05&amp;mode=TOC">Volume 5, August 1776March 1778</a>&gt; <a href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-05-02&amp;mode=TOC">Papers of John Adams</a>&gt; From James Lovell, 13 January 1778</div></div></div></div><div class="body-norm entry"><div class="printable-document"><a href="/founders/default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-05-02-0233&amp;printable=yes" style="font-weight:normal"><img style="border:0; vertical-align:text-bottom;" src="/img-ML/document-print.png" alt=""/> printable version</a><div class="header-arrows"><div class="header-comp-C1"><a class="point-prev" href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-05-02-0232" title="From Samuel and Robert Purviance, 9 January 1778"></a></div><div class="header-comp-C2"></div><div class="header-comp-C3"><a class="point-next" href="?keys=ADMS-print-06-05-02-0234&amp;mode=TOC" title="John Adams to the Speaker of the Massachusetts House of Representatives, with an Account of Adamss Expenses"></a></div></div><form style="display:inline" action="Utilities/goto-page-in-current-volume.xqy">
